This example runs PIMD for a benzene molecule solvated in a box of water.
The file `benzenebox.key` can be edited to choose the number of beads and a contraction scheme

NVT dynamics at 300K can be run with the command:
mpirun -np 1 path/to/pimd benzenebox 200000 2 1 2 300

NPT dynamics at 300K/1atm can be run with the command:
mpirun -np 1 path/to/pimd benzenebox 200000 2 1 4 300 1

